15. Attached hereto as Exhibit F is a true and correct copy of excerpts of text
messages between Dave Oder and me, as produced by Shift4 in this case. In one of those
text messages, dated [Date Redacted], Mr. Oder wrote: "Looks like one 5atanism down and one
to go[:]1 think FATT is ours now." Ex. F. I understood "5atanism"to be a reference to
[Redacted]. Oder replacing the letter "S" with the number "5."I understood the reference
"one . . . down and one to go" as referring to [Redacted] and [Redacted] respectively, [Redacted].
I understood the reference to "Fatt" to be the Fattmerchant account.
